---
layout: layout.njk
title: Mission Logs
description: Operational reports and technical logs from systems engineering, Rust development, and Unix infrastructure by Till Wegmüller (@toasterson)
---

<div class="space-y-10 animate-in">

    <!-- Header -->
    <section class="space-y-4">
        <div class="label-mono text-primary tracking-widest">ARCHIVE ACCESS</div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-grotesk font-bold text-on-surface text-bloom">
            Mission Logs
        </h1>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            Operational reports covering systems programming, kernel development,
            distribution packaging, and the occasional philosophical musing.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Log Entries -->
    <section class="space-y-0">
        {% for post in search.pages("type=post", "date=desc") %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="log-entry block group">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-2">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="status-dot flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-lg font-grotesk font-semibold text-on-surface group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                            {{ post.title }}
                        </h2>
                        <div class="label-mono text-on-surface-variant mt-1">
                            {{ post.date | date("yyyy.MM.dd") }}
                            {% if post.tags %}
                            &middot;
                            {% for tag in post.tags %}
                            <span class="text-tertiary">{{ tag }}</span>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}
                            {% endfor %}
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="label-mono text-on-surface-variant flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    {{ post.readingInfo.minutes }} min
                </div>
            </div>

            {% if post.summary %}
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm pl-[1.375rem] leading-relaxed">
                {{ post.summary }}
            </p>
            {% endif %}
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <!-- Archive Footer -->
    <section class="text-center space-y-4 pt-8">
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
            Technical posts covering OpenIndiana development, Rust programming,
            virtualization technologies, and Unix system administration.
        </p>
        <a href="/feed.xml" class="btn-secondary">
            Subscribe to Feed
        </a>
    </section>

</div>
